I think that&#x27;s a pretty extreme position. First, it will run a lot slower than the pattern matching alternative:<p><pre><code>    optional match {
      case Some(x) => whatever(x)
      case None    => fallback
    }
</code></pre>
Second, I find the pattern matching code much clearer. Sure, it&#x27;s also longer, but clarity trumps everything.
